data.title: Ella Fitzgerald Collection
data.meta_description: Ella Jane Fitzgerald, also known as 'the first lady of song,' is loved by jazz listeners worldwide. This collection features Fitzgerald's iconic wardrobe and highlights the stories and creators behind some of her famous clothing.
